      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23904,
      "text": "数学家真的给一类数起名叫做快乐数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "一个数快不快乐，取决于一场简单的迭代游戏。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "rule-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/xiaoxiao/rule-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "规则是：把这个数每一位的数字都平方，再全部加起来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "rule-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/xiaoxiao/rule-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "比如 19，就是 1 的平方加 9 的平方，等于 82。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "rule-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/xiaoxiao/rule-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23904,
      "text": "得到的新数继续这样算，一步接着一步。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "con-1",
      "filename": "converge-con-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/xiaoxiao/converge-con-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "有的数一路走下去，最终会稳稳地停在 1，这就是快乐数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "con-2",
      "filename": "converge-con-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/xiaoxiao/converge-con-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "19 就是这样：82、68、100，最后到 1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "con-3",
      "filename": "converge-con-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/xiaoxiao/converge-con-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "不快乐的数则会掉进一个固定的八数循环，永远出不来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "distribute",
      "line_id": "dis-1",
      "filename": "distribute-dis-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/xiaoxiao/distribute-dis-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "在 100 以内，快乐数大约有二十个，散落其间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "distribute",
      "line_id": "dis-2",
      "filename": "distribute-dis-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/xiaoxiao/distribute-dis-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25200,
      "text": "它们的分布看似杂乱，却藏着确定的规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "happy-numbers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/happy-numbers/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.16,
      "size": 34560,
      "text": "输入任意一个数，看它的迭代链是奔向 1，还是绕进循环。"
    },
    {
